sp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fila = row<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; columna = column<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; greatest = result<br /><br />print greatest, " en ", fila+1," , ", columna+1&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>#Revisar inclinadamente (en direcci&oacute;n de izquierda a derecha y hacia abajo)&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />for row in range(0,len(m)-3):<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; for column in range (0,len(m)-3):<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; result = m[row][column]*m[row+1][column+1]*m[row+2][column+2]*m[row+3][column+3]<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; if result &gt; greatest:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fila = row<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; columna = column<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; greatest = result<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />print greatest, " en ", fila+1," , ", columna+1</p>\r\n<p><br />#Inclinadamente de la otra forma, o sea, de derecha a izquierda, para abajo</p>\r\n<p>for row in range(3,len(m)):<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; for column in range (3,len(m)):<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; result = m[row][column]*m[row-1][column-1]*m[row-2][column-2]*m[row-3][column-3]<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; if result &gt; greatest:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fila = row<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; columna = column<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; greatest = result<br /><br />print greatest, " en ", fila+1," , ", columna+1</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>La matriz est&aacute; bien le&iacute;da, por as&iacute; decirlo.</p>'),
